pullRequest.title: [DOCS] Refreshes machine learning classification example
pullRequest.bodyText:
This PR refreshes the content in the classification analysis example (https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/machine-learning/master/flightdata-classification.html) to reflect things like (1) the addition of feature importance, (2) more details in the data frame analytics job stats, (3) changes to the filtering and appearance of the classification results.
Preview: http://stack-docs_1002.docs-preview.app.elstc.co/guide/en/machine-learning/master/flightdata-classification.html
